---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
  <Layout title="Stories">
    
  
<div class="bg-bertu-cream min-h-screen pt-32 pb-24 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    
    <h1 class="font-display text-[15vw] md:text-[8rem] font-black uppercase leading-[0.8] tracking-tighter text-bertu-black mb-16">
      Stories of Hope
    </h1>

    <section class="mb-24">
      <div class="flex justify-between items-end border-t-4 border-bertu-black pt-4 mb-8">
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-bertu-black tracking-tight">Top Stories</h2>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@bertumedia1" target="_blank" class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-bertu-orange hover:text-bertu-black transition-colors">All Stories &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-12 mb-12 items-start">
        <div class="lg:col-span-8 aspect-video w-full bg-bertu-black/5 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl">
          <iframe 
            class="w-full h-full"
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-UBgd2fMFao" 
            title="Bertu Media: The Hunger for Human Connection" 
            frameborder="0" 
            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" 
            allowfullscreen>
          </iframe>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-4 flex flex-col justify-center py-4">
          <p class="text-bertu-orange font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mb-3">Featured Documentary</p>
          <h3 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-[1.1] tracking-tight text-bertu-black mb-4">
            "I Am Hungry"
          </h3>
          <p class="text-bertu-black/70 font-sans text-lg mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            A heart-wrenching look at the life of an elderly man battling double kidney failure and blindness in total isolation. This documentary explores the devastating reality of being forgotten by society and the urgent need for communal compassion.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-bertu-black/40 text-sm font-medium">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 md:gap-6">
        <div class="flex flex-col group">
          <div class="aspect-video w-full bg-bertu-black/5 overflow-hidden mb-4">
            <iframe class="w-full h-full" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-fDzvNPsP28" title="Bertu Media: Ketera" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-bertu-black leading-tight mb-2 group-hover:text-bertu-orange transition-colors">
            The Beauty of Ketera in Addis Ababa
          </h4>
          <a  class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-bertu-black hover:text-bertu-orange transition-colors mt-auto pt-2">Watch Now &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col group">
          <div class="aspect-video w-full bg-bertu-black/5 overflow-hidden mb-4">
            <iframe class="w-full h-full" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/KuIY8PSIwuM" title="Bertu Media: Metal Worker" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-bertu-black leading-tight mb-2 group-hover:text-bertu-orange transition-colors">
            I Was a Top Student: The Amazing Metal Worker
          </h4>
          <a  class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-bertu-black hover:text-bertu-orange transition-colors mt-auto pt-2">Watch Now &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col group">
  <div class="aspect-video w-full bg-bertu-black/5 overflow-hidden mb-4 rounded-xl">
    <iframe 
      class="w-full h-full" 
      src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qWzu_K3csfc" 
      title="Bertu Media: Save a Mother's Life" 
      frameborder="0" 
      allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" 
      allowfullscreen>
    </iframe>
  </div>
  <h4 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-bertu-black leading-tight mb-2 group-hover:text-bertu-orange transition-colors">
    Saving a Mother: An Urgent Plea for Help
  </h4>
  <p class="text-bertu-black/60 text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed line-clamp-2">
    A mother of two is fighting for her life after three years of kidney failure. Her family has exhausted all resources; now, she needs our community to survive.
  </p>
  <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qWzu_K3csfc" target="_blank" class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-bertu-black hover:text-bertu-orange transition-colors mt-auto pt-2">
    Watch Now &rarr;
  </a>
</div>



    </section>

    <section class="mb-24">
      <div class="flex justify-between items-end border-t-4 border-bertu-black pt-4 mb-8">
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-bertu-black tracking-tight">Latest Reports</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div class="flex flex-col group">
          <div class="aspect-video w-full bg-bertu-black/5 overflow-hidden mb-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
            <iframe 
              class="w-full h-full" 
              src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/WeteoqDtULE" 
              title="Support for a Hero's Mother" 
              frameborder="0" 
              allowfullscreen>
            </iframe>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-bertu-black leading-tight mb-3 group-hover:text-bertu-orange transition-colors">
            Honoring a Hero's Sacrifice
          </h4>
          <p class="text-bertu-black/70 font-sans text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            A heartbreaking plea for the mother of a fallen soldier. Battling advanced cancer alone, she represents the silent struggles of those who gave everything for their country.
          </p>
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WeteoqDtULE" target="_blank" class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-bertu-orange hover:text-bertu-black transition-colors">Watch Report &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col group">
          <div class="aspect-video w-full bg-bertu-black/5 overflow-hidden mb-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
            <iframe 
              class="w-full h-full" 
              src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/nrclo9eXJ4E" 
              title="Zene's Story of Hope" 
              frameborder="0" 
              allowfullscreen>
            </iframe>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-bertu-black leading-tight mb-3 group-hover:text-bertu-orange transition-colors">
            From Tragedy to a New Life
          </h4>
          <p class="text-bertu-black/70 font-sans text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed">
             After surviving a life-threatening ordeal, Our sister was lifted from despair by your support. See her transformation as she opens her new business and finds hope again.
          </p>
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nrclo9eXJ4E" target="_blank" class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-bertu-orange hover:text-bertu-black transition-colors">Watch Full Story &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-24">
      <div class="flex justify-between items-end border-t-4 border-bertu-black pt-4 mb-8">
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-bertu-black tracking-tight">Global Updates</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="md:col-span-6 lg:col-span-5 flex flex-col justify-center order-2 md:order-1">
          <p class="text-bertu-orange font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mb-3">Breaking News</p>
          <h3 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-[1.1] tracking-tight text-bertu-black mb-4">
            California Wildfires Spreading Rapidly
          </h3>
          <p class="text-bertu-black/70 font-sans text-lg mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            An update covering the devastating wildfires sweeping across California at alarming speeds. Are these the signs of changing times?
          </p>
          <a  class="inline-flex items-center font-bold text-bertu-black hover:text-bertu-orange transition-colors group">
            Watch Full Coverage 
            <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right ml-2 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1 text-bertu-orange"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="md:col-span-6 lg:col-span-7 aspect-video w-full bg-bertu-black/5 overflow-hidden order-1 md:order-2">
          <iframe class="w-full h-full" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/4X27nBzsoik" title="Bertu Media: Wildfires" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div class="flex justify-between items-end border-t-4 border-bertu-black pt-4 mb-8">
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-bertu-black tracking-tight">Community Impact</h2>
        <a  class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-bertu-orange hover:text-bertu-black transition-colors">Our Initiatives &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
        <div class="lg:col-span-8">
          <div class="aspect-[16/10] w-full bg-bertu-black/10 overflow-hidden relative group">
            <img 
              src="./about_us_image.png" 
              alt="Community placeholder" 
              class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-4 flex flex-col justify-center">
          <p class="text-bertu-orange font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mb-3">Local Support</p>
          <h3 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold leading-[1.1] tracking-tight text-bertu-black mb-4">
            Expanding Youth Programs Across Addis Ababa
          </h3>
          <p class="text-bertu-black/70 font-sans text-lg mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Through targeted community funding and dedicated mentorship, local sports and leadership programs are seeing unprecedented growth in neighborhoods across the city.
          </p>
          
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</div>

</Layout>